```

I'm using a custom builder to inject some machine based environment variables using this in `angular.json`:

      "architect": {
        "build": {
          "builder": "@angular-builders/custom-webpack:browser",
          "options": {
            "customWebpackConfig": {
              "path": "extra-webpack.config.js"
          }, ...
